      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle, then take your<strong> chicken </strong>out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Add your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>ground coriander</strong>, <strong>dried oregano</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>cumin</strong>, a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and <strong>salt</strong> and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> to a plate and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>Cajun-style spice blend</strong></p>",
